# TempestDrop: System Architecture & Data Flow Diagram

## High-Level Mathematical Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant TargetOS as Victim OS (Windows)
    participant CoreTransmitter as Transmitter (Python/C++)
    participant AirGap as Physical Air-Gap (Optical)
    participant CameraAPI as Camera Sensor (Receiver)
    participant DSP as DSP Pipeline (NumPy/SciPy)
    participant Decoder as Protocol Decoder

    rect rgb(200, 150, 150)
    Note over TargetOS,CoreTransmitter: STAGE 1: INFECTION & ENCODING
    TargetOS->>CoreTransmitter: Read target file (e.g., id_rsa)
    CoreTransmitter->>CoreTransmitter: AES-256 Encrypt Payload (Optional)
    CoreTransmitter->>CoreTransmitter: Apply Hamming(7,4) Error Correction
    CoreTransmitter->>CoreTransmitter: Manchester Encoding (Clock Recovery)
    CoreTransmitter->>CoreTransmitter: Frame Construction (Preamble + Size + Data + CRC32)
    end

    rect rgb(150, 200, 150)
    Note over CoreTransmitter,AirGap: STAGE 2: PHYSICAL MODULATION
    loop Baseband Modulation (ASK)
        alt Bit == 1
            CoreTransmitter->>TargetOS: Win32 API SetMonitorBrightness(Base + Δ)
            TargetOS->>AirGap: Monitor Emits Photons (High Intensity)
        else Bit == 0
            CoreTransmitter->>TargetOS: Win32 API SetMonitorBrightness(Base - Δ)
            TargetOS->>AirGap: Monitor Emits Photons (Low Intensity)
        end
    end
    end

    rect rgb(150, 150, 200)
    Note over AirGap,CameraAPI: STAGE 3: OPTICAL CAPTURE
    loop Frame Acquisition (60 FPS)
        AirGap->>CameraAPI: Photons hit CMOS Sensor
        CameraAPI->>CameraAPI: Lock Auto-Exposure & Auto-Focus
        CameraAPI->>DSP: Push Raw RGB Frame Matrix (OpenCV)
    end
    end

    rect rgb(200, 200, 150)
    Note over DSP,Decoder: STAGE 4: DIGITAL SIGNAL PROCESSING
    loop Signal Extraction
        DSP->>DSP: Convert RGB -> Grayscale (Luma)
        DSP->>DSP: Define Region of Interest (ROI)
        DSP->>DSP: Calculate Spatial Mean Intensity: $\mu = \frac{1}{N} \sum_{i=1}^{N} I_i$
        DSP->>DSP: Append $\mu$ to Time-Series Buffer $s(t)$
        DSP->>DSP: Apply 4th-Order Butterworth Bandpass Filter to $s(t)$
        DSP->>DSP: Perform Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) for Carrier Lock
    end
    end

    rect rgb(150, 200, 200)
    Note over DSP,Decoder: STAGE 5: DEMODULATION & RECOVERY
    DSP->>Decoder: Pass Filtered Analog Signal $y(t)$
    Decoder->>Decoder: Schmitt Trigger Thresholding (Analog -> Digital)
    Decoder->>Decoder: Manchester Decoding (Phase Shift Recovery)
    Decoder->>Decoder: Sync to Preamble (0xAA)
    Decoder->>Decoder: CRC32 Validation
    alt CRC Valid
        Decoder->>TargetOS: Reconstruct Payload (id_rsa)
    else CRC Invalid
        Decoder->>Decoder: Request Retransmission / Wait for loop
    end
    end
```
